<item>
            <title>[LU-252] 2.6.37 removes bp arg from dump_trace()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-252</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The justification was that the bp argument is not necessary because the&lt;br/&gt;
combination of task and regs is sufficient to determine an appropriate&lt;br/&gt;
value for bp.  Red Hat backported this to 2.6.32-107.el6 so it has hit&lt;br/&gt;
current CHAOS kernels and will show up in RHEL 6.1.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
